import { useEffect, useState } from "react" export default function Users(){ const [users,setusers]=useState([]) useEffect(()=>{ fetch("http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/user/show") .then(res=>res.json()) .then(data=>setusers(data)) },[]) const ShowUsers=users.map((user,index)=> {index+1} {user.name} {user.email} ) return( {ShowUsers}
Id Users Email Acction
) }
